        {'instr':'Open `m365.cloud.microsoft/chat` > **Notebook** tab > **+ New Notebook**. Add the listed reference files, then paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Add 2 sources: /IR_01_Analyst_Consensus_Tracker.xlsx and /IR_04_Analyst_Engagement_Standards.docx. Set the Instruction: "You are my chief of staff. Cite source file and tab/section for every recommendation. Use a RAG framework for all output." Then ask the Notebook which analyst-consensus alignment priorities appear underfunded or mis-sequenced given current results, and which priorities should be accelerated, deferred, or stopped. Require Notebook to present the answer as a RAG table with rationale and source citation per row.'},
        {'instr':'Open `m365.cloud.microsoft/chat` > **Notebook** tab > **+ New Notebook**. Add the listed reference files, then paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Add 3 sources: /IR_01_Analyst_Consensus_Tracker.xlsx, /IR_03_IR_Disclosure_Playbook.docx and /IR_04_Analyst_Engagement_Standards.docx. Set the Instruction: "You are my governance reviewer. Identify contradictions across the 3 sources and present concise pre-reads for the Investor Relations Steering Committee." Then ask the Notebook to identify where the strategy narrative, the operational reality, and the policy obligations are misaligned ahead of the Investor Relations Steering Committee. Request a concise answer with 3 sections: Contradictions to Resolve, Questions Directors Will Ask, and Recommended Pre-Reads, all with citation to the source file.'}
