        {'instr':'', 'prompt':'After the Investor Relations Steering Committee has met, please complete in parallel: (1) draft the lender update email to our 3 lead relationship banks with the agreed messaging from the Investor Relations Steering Committee minutes; (2) draft the regulator holding note covering Bursa Malaysia continuous-disclosure rules and Securities Commission Malaysia guidance; (3) create a 30-day leadership task list covering analyst-consensus alignment recovery, supply risk discipline, cost takeout monitoring, and area-level recovery plans, then send it to the relevant function leads; (4) schedule a 20-minute checkpoint Teams meeting for this afternoon with the leadership team; (5) update the stakeholder communication tracker workbook with today\'s outreach. Wait for my confirmation before sending external emails.'}
