        {'instr':'Open a blank PowerPoint for Web file. Open the **Copilot pane** on the right. Paste the prompt below.', 'prompt':'Create a 5-slide Procurement Steering Committee deck on the 8.7% indirect-spend overrun and MYR 38M consolidation-savings shortfall using /PROC_01_Spend_Cube_Tracker.xlsx and /PROC_04_Vendor_Consolidation_Playbook.docx as source context. Cover: (1) sourcing discipline performance vs target, (2) the high-risk areas, (3) the likely root causes, (4) immediate management actions, (5) decisions required in 14 days. Use a serious executive design with the Group navy theme. Then use Edit with Copilot to add concise speaker notes for each slide, drop in a chart on slide 1 showing the variance, and tighten any slide with more than 30 words.'},
