        {'instr':'Open `m365.cloud.microsoft/chat` → **Agents** tab → choose **Word Agent**. Paste the prompt below — the agent returns a fully drafted `.docx` saved to OneDrive, ready to share. Works with the free Copilot Chat account or an M365 Copilot license.', 'prompt':'Generate a 2-page strategic reset briefing as a .docx using /IT_04_Cyber_Resilience_Playbook.docx and /IT_01_Availability_and_Cyber_Tracker.xlsx as context. Required sections: (1) IT priorities to Continue, (2) priorities to Reset, (3) priorities to Pause, with one-line rationale per item drawn from the workbook. Apply a clean executive layout and return the document as Cyber_Uplift_Reset_Briefing.docx.'}
